params.answerHashes: Hashes of the answers to the challenges in each path. For verification of storer's answer.
params.certHashes: Hashes of the certificates of the peers in the same order of selectedPs.
params.challengeHashes: Hashes of the challenges in each path (only encrypted by the recipient’s public key)
params.encWhisperKeys: Whisper keys of Owner for each path. Encrypted by the public key of each subsequent peer.
params.storerCertHashes: Hashes of the certificates of data storer.

setup(address[],uint256,uint256[],uint25.details: Lets owner set up the system.

params.deposit: The required deposit amount that is required of the selected peers.
params.pathEndings: For all paths, which index in selectedPeers that is the last peer for that path. E.g. If 3 then 2 is the last peer in the path.
params.remuneration: Total remuneration to the peers in all paths.
